cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.MA 

This paper proposes a new framework for modeling interaction with the environment in reinforcement learning, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also introduces a new learning algorithm, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG) and robotics (cs.RO). The framework and algorithm involve decision-making and optimization, which are relevant to control systems (cs.SY) and mathematical optimization (cs.MA).
